#. <section class="sutta" id="sn8.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga"
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Ānandasutta"
msgstr "4. With Ānanda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.405"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ānando sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Ānanda was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn8.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ "
"piṇḍāya pāvisi āyasmatā vaṅgīsena pacchāsamaṇena."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, "
"entered Sāvatthī for alms with Venerable Vaṅgīsa as his second monk."

msgctxt "sn8.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato vaṅgīsassa anabhirati uppannā hoti, rāgo "
"cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti."
msgstr ""
"And at that time Venerable Vaṅgīsa became dissatisfied, as lust infected his "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn8.4:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then he addressed Ānanda in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.1"
msgid "“Kāmarāgena ḍayhāmi,"
msgstr "“I’ve got a burning desire for pleasure;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.2"
msgid "cittaṃ me pariḍayhati;"
msgstr "My mind is on fire!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.3"
msgid "Sādhu nibbāpanaṃ brūhi,"
msgstr "Please, out of compassion, Gotama,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.4"
msgid "anukampāya gotamā”ti."
msgstr "tell me how to quench the flames.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.1"
msgid "“Saññāya vipariyesā,"
msgstr "“Your mind is on fire"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.2"
msgid "cittaṃ te pariḍayhati;"
msgstr "because of a perversion of perception."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.3"
msgid "Nimittaṃ parivajjehi,"
msgstr "Turn away from the aspect of things"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.4"
msgid "subhaṃ rāgūpasaṃhitaṃ."
msgstr "that’s attractive, provoking lust."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.1"
msgid "Saṅkhāre parato passa,"
msgstr "See all conditioned phenomena as other,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.2"
msgid "dukkhato mā ca attato;"
msgstr "as suffering and not-self."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.3"
msgid "Nibbāpehi mahārāgaṃ,"
msgstr "Extinguish the great fire of lust,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.4"
msgid "mā ḍayhittho punappunaṃ."
msgstr "don’t burn up again and again."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.406"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.1"
msgid "Asubhāya cittaṃ bhāvehi,"
msgstr "Meditate on the unattractive,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.2"
msgid "ekaggaṃ susamāhitaṃ;"
msgstr "unified, serene;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.3"
msgid "Sati kāyagatā tyatthu,"
msgstr "with mindfulness immersed in the body,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.4"
msgid "nibbidābahulo bhava."
msgstr "be full of disillusionment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.1"
msgid "Animittañca bhāvehi,"
msgstr "Meditate on the signless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.2"
msgid "mānānusayamujjaha;"
msgstr "give up the underlying tendency to conceit;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.3"
msgid "Tato mānābhisamayā,"
msgstr "and when you comprehend conceit,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.4"
msgid "upasanto carissasī”ti."
msgstr "you will live at peace.”"
